room_title: Escape room "Mystery of the Pharaoh" by Wake Forest Escape Room in Raleigh - Durham
room_address: 10501 Ligon Mill Rd #102 Wake Forest, NC 27587
room_description: Your Archaeological team’s quest is to unlock the Pharaoh’s Tomb. Other teams have attempted and vanished during their search. The Ancient Egyptians were known for their mystical ways, opulence, and power. Upon the death of a pharaoh, the corpse was enclosed inside a sarcophagus, with provisions for the afterlife. Work together with your team to find the tomb and escape.
